'''Hancc Rellow''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] noble and member of the [[Dentaalian House]].

After the House of Dentaal was disbanded by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Taliff]], he founded the [[Dentaal Independence Party]] that [[Dentaal Uprising|overthrew]] him. However, he was killed with the rest of the planet's population when the Empire released [[Candorian plague/Legends|Candorian plague]] on Dentaal.

